# Commit message template
# Use this template to write commit messages in the project's preferred style.
# Example: "Fix: Upgrade to latest Next.js"

# Format:
# <Type>: <Short Title Case Description>
#
# Optional body (more details, motivation, what changed).
#
# Footer: (e.g. issue refs, breaking changes)
#
# Allowed Types: Fix, Feat, Chore, Docs, Style, Refactor, Test, Perf, Ci

<type>: <Short Title Case Description>


Optional longer description (wrap at ~72 chars).

Footer: Closes/Refs: #<issue-number> (optional)
